    "name": "존슨앤드존슨 ",
    "image": "https://daoift3qrrnil.cloudfront.net/employment_companies/images/000/043/780/original/%EC%A1%B4%EC%8A%A8%EC%95%A4%EB%93%9C%EC%A1%B4%EC%8A%A8_%EB%A1%9C%EA%B3%A0.png?1618216616",
    "start_time": "2021-04-01T17:27:00.000+09:00",
    "end_time": "2021-04-14T23:59:00.000+09:00",
    "content": "<div style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; color: #333; font-size: 15px; word-break: break-word;\">\r\n<div style=\"padding: 6%;\">\r\n<div style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; background: #fafafa; padding: 10px; text-align: center; font-size: 20px; color: #000; font-weight: bold;\">[얀센 백신] Business Management Support &amp; General Manager Assistant</div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center; height: 150px; margin: 14% auto;\"><img src=\"https://daoift3qrrnil.cloudfront.net/business_employment_companies/images/000/007/841/original/%EC%A1%B4%EC%8A%A8%EC%95%A4%EB%93%9C%EC%A1%B4%EC%8A%A8_%EB%A1%9C%EA%B3%A0.png?1618216176\" style=\"max-height:120px; max-width:40% !important;\" /></div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"color: #000;\">\r\n<div>Johnson &amp; Johnson is the world`s most comprehensive and broadly based healthcare Company, touching the lives of nearly a billion people every day. Our Family of Companies throughout the world compete in consumer, pharmaceutical, and medical devices and diagnostics markets and have the skills and resources to tackle the worlds most pressing health issues.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"padding: 6%; border-top: 1px solid #ddd; border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;\">\r\n<div style=\"font-size: 16px; color: #000; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 10px;\">&bull; 모집 직무</div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"margin-bottom: 20px;\">\r\n<div style=\"font-size: 16px; color: #000; font-weight: bold;\">[얀센 백신] Business Management Support &amp; General Manager Assistant (계약직)</div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"margin-top: 10px;\">\r\n<div>Johnson &amp; Johnson is the world&#39;s most comprehensive and broadly based healthcare Company, touching the lives of nearly a billion people every day. Our Family of Companies throughout the world compete in consumer, pharmaceutical, and medical devices and diagnostics markets and have the skills and resources to tackle the world&#39;s most pressing health issues.</div>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div>- 계열사: Janssen Vaccines</div>\r\n\r\n<div>- 포지션: Business Management Support &amp; General Manager Assistant</div>\r\n\r\n<div>- 근무지: 인천 송도</div>\r\n\r\n<div>- 근무형태: Fixed Term</div>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div>[Summary]</div>\r\n\r\n<div>This position seeks for a future leader who will be able to multitask in both administrative support to General Manager and business management &amp; organization development to the site leadership team with high energy and willingness to try with fresh ideas. In parallel, we seek for this person to communicate internally and externally to enhance the site culture.</div>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div>[Responsibilities]</div>\r\n\r\n<div>- Provide a wide range of administrative and secretarial support to General Manager such as internal &amp; external communication and interaction with executives and site calendar management.</div>\r\n\r\n<div>- Support major site events and activities including workshops, internal &amp; external meetings, and guests visits.</div>\r\n\r\n<div>- Manage Internal site communication through Site advertisement, notice board, and welcome screen, etc.</div>\r\n\r\n<div>- Monitor external media monitoring &amp; business performance review</div>\r\n\r\n<div>- Closely work with Business Excellence to support business management</div>\r\n\r\n<div>- Involve in Organizational Development perspective to enhance site culture and to support change initiatives.</div>\r\n\r\n<div>- Regular administrative work such as office supplies management, expense processing, and company seal management</div>\r\n\r\n<div>- Adhere to strict confidentiality requirements of business, personnel, and sensitive information.</div>\r\n\r\n<div>- Provide direct support for the annual meeting of shareholders and notarization process of minutes thereof.</div>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div>[Requirements]</div>\r\n\r\n<div>- Fluent in English and Korean; good oral and written communication skills.</div>\r\n\r\n<div>- Able to work as a team with collaborative mindset and ownership.</div>\r\n\r\n<div>- Has an attitude of willingness to learn.</div>\r\n\r\n<div>- Time management skill is critical.</div>\r\n\r\n<div>- Proactive and quick learner</div>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div>[지원 방법]</div>\r\n\r\n<div>www.careers.jnj.com -&gt; Requisition number 2105908338W검색 -&gt; 해당 모집 공고 클릭 후, &ldquo;Apply Now&rdquo; 클릭 후 온라인 지원 프로세스 진행</div>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div>[제출 서류]</div>\r\n\r\n<div>국문 형식의 이력서와 자기소개서 (필수)/ 영문 이력서와 자기소개서 (Optional)</div>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div>[서류 마감일]</div>\r\n\r\n<div>2021년 4월 14일까지&nbsp;&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div>[For more Johnson &amp; Johnson]</div>\r\n\r\n<div>- J&amp;J Company Page: http://www.jobkorea.co.kr/Company/1605233/Info</div>\r\n\r\n<div>- J&amp;J Korea Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/JNJCareersKorea/</div>\r\n\r\n<div>- J&amp;J Korea Linkedin: https://www.linkedin.com/company/johnson-&amp;-johnson/</div>\r\n\r\n<div>- 존슨앤드존슨 오픈 포지션 및 다양한 소식들을 기업관 페이지, 페이스북, 링크드인 페이지를 통해 만나 보시기 바랍니다.&nbsp;&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div>[유의사항]</div>\r\n\r\n<div>- 서류를 MS-Word 나 PDF 로 된 한 개의 파일로 미리 준비하시기 바랍니다.</div>\r\n\r\n<div>- 서류 전형 합격자에 한하여 개별 통보합니다. 단, 회사 사정에 따라 지연될 수 있습니다.</div>\r\n\r\n<div>- 모집 분야 관련하여 자세한 내용은 J&amp;J 홈페이지에서 확인하시기 바랍니다.</div>\r\n\r\n<div>www.careers.jnj.com</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"padding: 6%;\">\r\n<div style=\"font-size: 16px; color: #000; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 10px;\">&bull; 근무환경</div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"margin-bottom: 20px;\">\r\n<div>상기참조</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"font-size: 16px; color: #000; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 10px;\">&bull; 접수 경로</div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"margin-bottom: 20px;\">careers.jnj.com</div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"font-size: 16px; color: #000; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 10px;\">&bull; 제출 서류</div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"margin-bottom: 20px;\">국문 형식의 이력서와 자기소개서 (필수)/ 영문 이력서와 자기소개서 (Optional)</div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"font-size: 16px; color: #000; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 10px;\">&bull; 문의처</div>\r\n\r\n<div>존슨앤드존슨채용팀/recruitment-jnj@its.jnj.com</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n"
